comment_text:
@Susan  the first 3 days were horrible, full on hives (covered in swollen wheals), almost gave up and took an a/h but somehow got through it. By day 4 feeling much better wheals almost gone. Day 5 – clear. Now on day 18 with no hive flare ups at all. If this is all it takes to cure hives, I'm sticking with it!!! :)
